lead_paragraph: Cuba's Yarelys Barrios has been stripped of the silver medal she won in the discus at the Beijing Olympics after failing a doping re-test, the International Olympic Committee (IOC) said on Thursday.

headline.print_headline: Doping-Cuban Discus Thrower Barrios Stripped of Beijing Silver Medal
